{"tid":1738350,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母曾鈺成張達明 如在場人士希望離開 可保障各位不受暴力對待?","createTime":"2019-11-19T08:23:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T08:27:18.000Z","uid":220864,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"75b5e69163c40524ffd0e2e45bdb6091b62df9cc","tid":1738350,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:23:06.000Z","msg":"幾撚時暴力對待係必然發生<br />\n要你班撚樣入嚟保障<br />\n<br />\n你明知班狗無人性暴力對待示威者<br />\n你唔撚去屌班狗<br />\n你入嚟扮好人話保障到佢地?<br />\n屌你老母原來不受暴力對待呢樣野係香港係要知名人士去保障<br />\n你自己講得出都知咩事啦<br />\n重合理化成件事<br />\n當自己係英雄?<br />\n明明你係蹤容緊班狗呀垃圾"},{"pid":"2be44ebda0cbdf2168ec9b24ece52c448350117a","tid":1738350,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:23:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8415b5f661e637a17319bd21a181370b778d70a","tid":1738350,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:23:48.000Z","msg":"嬲撚到"},{"pid":"af9312f2940f68d0dcb81923afb0432dba90f44a","tid":1738350,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:25:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d18c91c223e745816b31cbf4c58a5950270c82","tid":1738350,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:25:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5fd8a7ef71d4b2a7db936f28bf6a84a59ff821","tid":1738350,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:26:16.000Z","msg":"尋日又無人屌架喎"},{"pid":"94365eb0d5bdd7d3aa550e7c51c8245ab1d07fb0","tid":1738350,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:27:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}